                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Terms & Conditions</h5>

                                        <ul>
                                        <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">All the information you need for a seamless experience with Freshly Meals. These Terms and Conditions apply to Freshly Meals and all its subsidiaries and partners. For the purpose of these Terms and Conditions, wherever the context so requires “You” or “Client” shall mean any natural or legal person who visits our Website/App and engages to buy our products. The term “We”, “Us”, “Our” shall mean Freshly Meals.</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">The Terms & Conditions was last updated on 30 November 2022.</li>
                                        </ul>


                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">General Terms</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Clients that have signed up with Freshly Meals have agreed to Terms and Conditions during their subscription with Us. Freshly Meals reserves the right to update or amend these Terms and Conditions, at its sole discretion, without prior notice.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Further, the Terms and Conditions may be changed or updated as and when required to meet any changes in the requirements and standards as per applicable laws. We encourage You to frequently visit these sections to be updated on any changes made on Our platforms and to remain in compliance with these terms.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Payments & Refunds</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">We accept online payments via credit / debit card. </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Payment must be made in full, 72 working hours before the chosen delivery date. Deliveries will not be processed unless the payment is received in full. In case a payment is declined either by your bank, credit/debit card or other payment modes, we won’t be able to dispatch the delivery.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">All discounted plans have a NO REFUND policy. If you wish to subscribe with us, then we would suggest you take a 3-day trial and test the service (meal options, meal portions, meal flavours/spice/salt levels, delivery timings etc.) before committing on a full month plan.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">If you do wish to cancel your subscription, all full price plans (without any discounts) will incur a twenty percent (20%) cancellation fee on the remaining number of days. All cancellations will be processed by Us 72 hours (or 3 working days) after the request is received.  Your balance refund will be processed on the 30th of every month after the request is received through our app or informed to our customer service team via our chat support.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">A refundable deposit of AED 100 is charged per subscription for the insulated bags. Failure to return the insulated bag will result in forfeiture of the bag deposit. Additionally, for each missing bag and/or ice packs, a deduction of AED 50 will be applied.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">As for the refund of insulated bags & ice packs, these need to be returned before the 30th of every month to process the refund. Cancellations will be processed on the 30th day of every month after the request is received from the Client through our app.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">All refunds shall be processed to the client’s bank account. The client needs to provide his full name, email address, bank name, bank address, IBAN & account number to process the refund via the app.</li>
                                        </ul>


                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:28px;text-align:center;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 3px solid #03696D; display: inline; padding-bottom: 5px;">Your Meal Plan</h5>

                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Ordering</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">If You place an order through any of Our online channels, chat support, payment links etc., You are responsible for checking and confirming your order details (i.e., meal plan selected, food selections based on your taste and preferences, allergies, delivery dates, timings, delivery locations etc.). </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Products and services displayed on the website/app may not constitute an offer to sell. Orders placed by You are offers to purchase particular product under these Terms and Conditions at the price specified (including delivery and other charges). We reserve the right to accept or reject your offer for any reason (or no reason) including, but not limited to, the unavailability of any product, an error in the price or product description, or an error in your order.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">The product images displayed on the Freshly Meals app are only for reference purpose. While every reasonable effort is made to maintain accuracy of information on the app, actual product packaging, product size, finish, colour, and such other product details may vary than what is shown on the app. Freshly Meals hereby disclaims any guarantees of exactness as to the taste, finish, appearance, size, colour etc., of the food product as ordered by You.</li>
                                        </ul>

                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Subscriptions, Prices & Payments</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">We have daily, weekly, or monthly subscriptions for You to choose from based on your plan, number of meals etc. For the purposes of Our weekly and monthly subscriptions, a week constitutes a maximum of 6 calendar days, a month constitutes a maximum of 24 calendar days.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Pricing is based on the plan You choose the number of meals You opt for, and the number of deliveries You require, each week. The Freshly Meals app will give You a complete order summary along with 5% VAT, delivery charges, discount offers and any other charges as applicable. </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">All Our subscriptions (whether daily, weekly, or monthly) incur advance payments.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Altering Your Plan - Pause/Renew</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">You may make any alternations to your meal plan service (i.e., change in menu, delivery address, pausing your current plan, renewing your current/new plan etc.) by providing a prior notice of 72 working hours (3 working days) through our app. Changes can be made from your login page on the iOS / Android app only within that time-period.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        {{-- <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Cancelling Your Plan</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">You may cancel your plan through the option provided on the Freshly Meals app.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">All cancellations will be processed by Us 48 hours (or two working days) after the request is received.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Cancellations will be processed on the 30th day of every month after the request is received from the Client through our app. A 20% cancellation fee on the total billed
                                            amount is applicable in case of all cancellations. The insulated bags along with the ice
