                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Meal Plan Validity</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">All plans have a 1 additional month (30 days) validity period from the day of your first delivery. You can pause and re-start your plan any number of times within this given period. Your subscription amount will be forfeited if You do not complete your package within this duration.</li>
                                        </ul>

                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:28px;text-align:center;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 3px solid #03696D; display: inline; padding-bottom: 5px;">Delivery & Storage</h5>

                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 20px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Daily Delivery Schedules</h5>

                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">We use a third-party delivery service provider and offer deliveries six days a week across the United Arab Emirates. Your details (name, address, Google Maps location, and mobile number) are shared with the service provider. Please check Our delivery locations before placing your order and select your delivery timings based on your location and preference (Your food deliveries are daily and can arrive within the given selected time slot). A Freshly Meals representative will contact You with information about delivery to your chosen delivery location within 24 hrs.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">We do not take responsibility for any failure to deliver due to inaccurate address details and refunds cannot be claimed in such case.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">We shall use best efforts to deliver the food/ meal to You as per the timelines mentioned on the Freshly Meals app, however, the delivery time mentioned on app is merely an estimate and the actual delivery time may vary, and is subject to inter alia weather and traffic conditions, delivery address distance. Further, We shall not be responsible any loss or delays affected by any political or social scenarios, beyond Our control, such as lockdowns, road diversions or any other impediments of like nature.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Your Insulated Bag</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">In order to avoid spoilage, Our food is delivered in insulated bags, lined with ice packs. The Food will be delivered by the delivery partner outside your delivery location. Our delivery partners will not ring your doorbell unless specifically requested.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Freshly Meals will not be held liable for spoilage, theft, and / or damage caused by others. The risk of loss for such products passes on to You upon delivery.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">For best results and to avoid food spoilage, please refrigerate the food no more than two hours after delivery and consume within 24 hours.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Empty bags are to be left outside your delivery location for Our delivery partners to collect on your next delivery.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Health Claims</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Weight loss, muscle gain, weight management and other information mentioned on any of Our platforms is for informational purposes only and no benefits or results are guaranteed or assured. Your results may vary based on multiple factors such as genetics, lifestyle habits, activity levels, sleeping patterns, etc. Freshly Meals does not provide information that has been medically validated. We are not a medical organization, and the information mentioned on any of Our platforms should not be misconstrued as medical advice, prescriptions, or diagnoses. Please consult your doctor before subscribing to a meal plan, or when making any changes to the plan that might affect your health.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Food Allergies, Preferences, Heating Instructions & Safety</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Freshly Meals is not responsible for undeclared allergies / intolerances. Clients are expected to select the dishes themselves based on their preferences and requirements. For customization requirements, we cater to 3 allergens & 3 dislikes in the plan. If any dish or an ingredient is requested which is not in the kitchen facility, the client shall be charged for the same.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">For best results and to avoid food spoilage, please refrigerate the food no more than two hours after delivery and consume within 24 hours.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Our food boxes are microwave safe. You must remove the lid from the food boxes before re-heating.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Nutritional values shared across Our plans and meals are an indicative range, derived from the USDA database by formulating each ingredient per dish and set. Any information provided by Freshly Meals in reference to this is not intended to diagnose, treat, or cure any health condition. We hereby disclaim any and all liability in connection therewith.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">The content of the Freshly Meals app, including without limitation, text, copy, audio, video, photographs, illustrations, graphics and other visuals, is for informational purposes only and does not constitute/substitute professional medical advice, diagnosis, treatment or recommendations of any kind. You should always seek the advice of your qualified heath care professionals with any questions or concerns You may have regarding your individual needs and any medical conditions. You agree that You will not under any circumstances disregard any professional medical advice or delay in seeking such advice in reliance on any content provided on or through the Freshly Meals App. Reliance on any such content is solely at your own risk.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">Freshly Meals production facility produces food across all major food allergies that is determined by the U.S. Food & Drug Administration i.e. milk, eggs, soya, fish, shellfish, peanuts, tree nuts, gluten etc. Cross contamination may unintentionally occur during production or packaging, which may cause your meals to contain some or all of the above-mentioned allergens. If You feel uncomfortable after consuming any of Our meals, consult your doctor immediately. Freshly Meals does not take any responsibility for any adverse effects on your health, or medical conditions or extremities that may be experienced during the tenure of the meal delivery or at any time thereafter. Any damages, monetary losses on such account will not be borne by Us.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <h5 style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-top: 10px; font-size:22px;text-align:left;color:#03696D;font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;font-weight: 700;">Privacy, Content, Proprietary Rights, Trademark</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">All credit / debit card details and personal identifiable information will NOT be stored, sold, shared, rented or leased to any third parties.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li style="text-align: left; color: #455056; font-size: 15px;">All right, title and interest in usage of the copyrights, patents, content (images, copy, nutritional information, calories etc.) shall belong solely and exclusively to Freshly Meals. Freshly Meals logo, product names, feature names, designs etc. are a trademark of Freshly Meals and may not be used, copied, reproduced, republished, uploaded, or imitated without the prior consent of Freshly Meals.</li>
                                        </ul>

